<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201130/79c36725907e4099ba860e25d4082b2e.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>分红时的喜悦（央广网记者 郭长江 摄）</span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span><span><span><span>丁支书给我说，</span></span></span><span><span><span>‘</span></span></span><span><span><span>不行了你买两头大母牛吧</span></span></span><span><span><span>’</span></span></span><span><span><span>。我说，</span></span></span><span><span><span>‘</span></span></span><span><span><span>现在没钱</span></span></span><span><span><span>’</span></span></span><span><span><span>。他说，</span></span></span><span><span><span>‘</span></span></span><span><span><span>钱你不要愁了</span></span></span><span><span><span>’</span></span></span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span><span><span><span>就</span></span></span><span><span><span>给我赊了</span></span></span><span><span><span>那</span></span></span><span><span><span>两头</span></span></span><span><span><span>黑白花的基础母牛</span></span></span><span><span><span>。我就从那两头现在发展到17头。昨天6万6卖掉了3头。</span></span></span><span><span><span>”李向兵说，他家的牛能养到今天这个情况，离不开丁建华</span></span></span><span><span><span>的鼓励和帮助。</span></span></span><span><span><span>平日里，</span></span></span><span><span><span>只要</span></span></span><span><span><span>因为</span></span></span><span><span><span>牛的事情</span></span></span><span><span><span>给丁书记打电话，</span></span></span><span><span><span>他立马就到。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
